. *************** Export TeX Table ****************
. *************************************************
. 
. *** Panel A: Covered sectors
. esttab c1 c2 c3 c4 c5 ///
>     using "../../paper/tables/did-wage-sector-`ds'.tex", replace label fragme
> nt ///
